title: Volvo car sales in Sweden 2009 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Units sold. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
Overall Units sold has increased over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2009 and 2010.
The highest Units sold, of value 75506.0 was reached at Year 2017
The lowest Units sold, of value 41808.0 was reported at Year 2009
min_summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Units sold, containing a total of 11 data points.
Overall Units sold has increased over the Year.

Units sold is slightly increasing from 2009 to 2010, roughly decreasing from 2010 to 2011, roughly constant from 2011 to 2013, slightly increasing from 2013 to 2015, roughly constant from 2015 to 2017, and finally slightly decreasing from 2017 to 2019.
